data.title: queen’s police medal – Police Digital Service
data.text:
Tony Blaker QPM has been announced as Interim Director of Delivery Services for the Police Digital Service (PDS). Tony joined PDS as Senior Responsible Owner in 2021, leading on Criminal Justice Transformation including work on Serious Sexual Offences, Digital Case File, Video Enabled Policing and Digital Forensics. Prior to his role with PDS Tony had […]

Read More

The Police Digital Service is a partner to UK policing and law enforcement organisations. Please note, we are NOT a police force and can not handle public enquiries. Contact the police by calling 999 to report emergencies or call 101 for non-emergencies. Find your local force and report online via www.police.uk.
